otwendig erscheint und wie man Innovation und Tradition sinnvoll verbinden kann.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 17. Dez 2021) 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / General.2bisacsh  aBildung.  aFamilie.  aFinanzinnovation.  aGesellschaft.  aKreativität.  aMünchener Innovationsgruppe.  aPsychologie.  aWissensmanagement.  aÖffentliche Verwaltung.1 aFisch, Rudolf, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aFrey, Dieter, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aFrey, Dieter, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aHense, Jan, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aLern, Andreas, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMandl, Heinz, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMandl, Heinz, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aOerter, Rolf, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aOerter, Rolf, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aRosenstiel, Lutz von, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aRosenstiel, Lutz, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aSchneewind, Klaus A., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSchneewind, Klaus A., eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Social Sciences 2000 - 2014z9783110638080oZDB-23-GSS08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruyterteBook-Paket Best of Lucius & Luciusz97831105150770 cprintz978382820499740uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311051008940uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110510089423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783110510089/original  a978-3-11-051507-7  eBook-Paket Best of Lucius &